OL,3,CBirmingham Airport recruits more
OL,4,Cworkers after 'painful' rule change
OL,6,FBirmingham Airport has recruited 100
OL,7,Fstaff members in a bid to deal with
OL,8,Fthe fall-out over a sudden UK liquid
OL,9,Frule change.
OL,11,FIt comes just a week after airport
OL,12,Fchief executive Nick Barton spoke to
OL,13,FITV News Central Presenter Sameena Ali-
OL,14,FKhan and explained what the long-term
OL,15,Fplan is to help combat the long queues
OL,16,Fand lengthy wait times.
