OL,3,CBirmingham Airport recruits more
OL,4,Cworkers after 'painful' rule change
OL,6,FMr Barton said BHX has hired
OL,7,Fspecialist 'liquids consultants', to
OL,8,Fmonitor every single entrance to the
OL,9,Fairport and help passengers get their
OL,10,Fbags ready for the security hall.
OL,12,FThe travel boss confirmed 100 new
OL,13,Fstaff members have been drafted in as
OL,14,Fthe airport works to stem queues at
OL,15,Fpeak times. The staff will be based
OL,16,Fbefore any scanners to help ensure
OL,17,Fpassengers are only carrying 100ml
OL,18,Fcontainers of liquid.
