OL,3,CBirmingham Airport recruits more
OL,4,Cworkers after 'painful' rule change
OL,6,FThis comes as the airport says
OL,7,Fincorrect volumes of liquids have been
OL,8,Fpartly responsible for delaying
OL,9,Fpassengers this week, along with a
OL,10,Flast-minute government change to
OL,11,Fliquid rules for carry-on hand
OL,12,Fluggage, described as "painful" by Mr
OL,13,FBarton.
OL,15,FMany have called for an urgent re-
OL,16,Fthink to get the terminal in order
OL,17,Fahead of the anticipated summer
OL,18,Fholiday rush, as the airport deals
OL,19,Fwith a change in liquid rules,
OL,20,Ftraveller confusion, and restricted
OL,21,Fqueueing space.
