OL,3,CBirmingham Airport recruits more
OL,4,Cworkers after 'painful' rule change
OL,6,FMr Barton explained their ribbon
OL,7,Fcutting 'ta-da' moment crumbled last
OL,8,Fweek when a new UK Government
OL,9,Fdirective landed on their desk to
OL,10,Finsist passengers only carry liquids,
OL,11,Fpastes and gels up to 100ml in their
OL,12,Fhand luggage.
OL,14,FBHX had anticipated that by June 1,
OL,15,Fthe 2 litre rule would come into force.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
