OL,3,CBirmingham Airport recruits more
OL,4,Cworkers after 'painful' rule change
OL,6,FBut government transport chiefs
OL,7,Fannounced they needed to re-validate
OL,8,Fall the software on every machine
OL,9,F(including at other UK airports such
OL,10,Fas London City, which had already
OL,11,Frolled out the 2 litre allowance).
OL,13,FThat, combined with ongoing building
OL,14,Fworks and those who still mistakenly
OL,15,Fbring through more than 100ml, say
OL,16,FBHX, is causing a major hold up to
OL,17,Freach the scanners, particularly
OL,18,Fduring the peak morning rush.
