OL,3,CBirmingham Airport recruits more
OL,4,Cworkers after 'painful' rule change
OL,6,FWith no answer given from the
OL,7,Fgovernment on when software validation
OL,8,Fwill be completed on the pricey
OL,9,Fsecurity kit, BHX has recruited the
OL,10,Fextra staff to help customers transit
OL,11,Fmore smoothly through to departures.
OL,13,FMr Barton insisted they are hopeful
OL,14,Fthat the situation will ease with the
OL,15,Fsteps they are taking: "We definitely
OL,16,Fwant to improve from where we are and
OL,17,Fwe will."
